.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-EXAMPLES" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-examples \- Search shipped examples and starter templates
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose examples [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
List, search, and render a coverage table for shipped hpc\-compose examples and built\-in starter templates.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBlist\fR
List shipped examples and starter templates. See hpc\-compose\-examples\-list(1).
.TP
\fBsearch\fR
Search shipped examples and starter templates. See hpc\-compose\-examples\-search(1).
.TP
\fBrecommend\fR
Recommend starting examples for a workflow. See hpc\-compose\-examples\-recommend(1).
.TP
\fBcoverage\fR
Print the examples coverage table used by the docs. See hpc\-compose\-examples\-coverage(1).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose examples list
hpc\-compose examples list \-\-tag mpi \-\-format json
hpc\-compose examples search 'vllm worker'
hpc\-compose examples recommend 'multi\-node training' \-\-tag gpu
hpc\-compose examples recommend \-\-format json
hpc\-compose examples coverage \-\-format markdown
.fi
